A wonderful wooden dispenser by Japanese brand Kukkia. Who hasn’t always wanted their very own vending machine?

Turn the star and see what comes next ! You will not want to stop turning until your favourite piece comes out. If one gets stuck, just give it a shake!

Perfect for role play and displaying in your child’s room!

  • Contents – 45 wooden beads and shapes (please refer to image for specific quantities)
  • Please note – due to the natural wood material, it may show natural occurring imperfections which is completely normal.
  • For ages 3+
  • Material – Beech wood (body), Chinese local wood (beads & shapes), PET plastic case
  • Size: 12cm x 12cm x 20cm
Weight 1.3 kg
Dimensions 13 × 14 × 23 cm
